		<title>20HOME LIFE</title>
		<content>{FOOD}                                 
 North East of Scotland Recipes        
                                       
{SKIRLIE                               
 3 Handfuls oatmeal; 500 g.  Suet; 2   
 Onions (chopped); Salt and Pepper.    
 METHOD                                
 Brown the onions with suet.  Add the  
 oatmeal and seasoning and fry till    
 brown.                                
                                       
{BROSE                                 
 Oatmeal; Salt and Pepper.             
 METHOD                                
 Mix ingredients in bowl and add       
 sufficient boiling water to wet       
 thoroughly.  Stir well and let stand  
 to allow the brose to swell.  Do not  
 let it get cold.  Excellent with rich 
 milk or cream.                        
                                       
